{
  "video_id": "FPhZGD-6kVQ",
  "title": "4 ways to build a human company in the age of machines | Tim Leberecht",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12560.0,
      "end_time": 16136.0,
      "text": "Half of the human workforce is expected to be replaced"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16160.0,
      "end_time": 18880.0,
      "text": "by software and robots in the next 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19480.0,
      "end_time": 23680.0,
      "text": "And many corporate leaders welcome that as a chance to increase profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24600.0,
      "end_time": 26816.0,
      "text": "Machines are more efficient;"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26840.0,
      "end_time": 30800.0,
      "text": "humans are complicated and difficult to manage."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31720.0,
      "end_time": 37176.0,
      "text": "Well, I want our organizations to remain human."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37200.0,
      "end_time": 40000.0,
      "text": "In fact, I want them to become beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 41120.0,
      "end_time": 44735.0,
      "text": "Because as machines take our jobs and do them more efficiently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44759.0,
      "end_time": 48976.0,
      "text": "soon the only work left for us humans will be the kind of work"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 49000.0,
      "end_time": 53800.0,
      "text": "that must be done beautifully rather than efficiently."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 53760.0,
      "end_time": 56936.0,
      "text": "To maintain our humanity in the this second Machine Age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 56960.0,
      "end_time": 60960.0,
      "text": "we may have no other choice than to create beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62240.0,
      "end_time": 64456.0,
      "text": "Beauty is an elusive concept."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 64480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67880.0,
      "text": "For the writer Stendhal it was the promise of happiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 68520.0,
      "end_time": 70856.0,
      "text": "For me it&#39;s a goal by Lionel Messi."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 70880.0,
      "end_time": 72295.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 72320.0,
      "end_time": 73895.0,
      "text": "So bear with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73920.0,
      "end_time": 78296.0,
      "text": "as I am proposing four admittedly very subjective principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 78320.0,
      "end_time": 81240.0,
      "text": "that you can use to build a beautiful organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81960.0,
      "end_time": 84496.0,
      "text": "First: do the unnecessary."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84520.0,
      "end_time": 85735.0,
      "text": "[Do the Unnecessary]"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85760.0,
      "end_time": 87296.0,
      "text": "A few months ago, Hamdi Ulukaya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 87320.0,
      "end_time": 90455.0,
      "text": "the CEO and founder of the yogurt company Chobani,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90480.0,
      "end_time": 95400.0,
      "text": "made headlines when he decided to grant stock to all of his 2,000 employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95600.0,
      "end_time": 97536.0,
      "text": "Some called it a PR stunt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97560.0,
      "end_time": 99776.0,
      "text": "others -- a genuine act of giving back."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99800.0,
      "end_time": 102480.0,
      "text": "But there is something else that was remarkable about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103000.0,
      "end_time": 105560.0,
      "text": "It came completely out of the blue."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 105800.0,
      "end_time": 107696.0,
      "text": "There had been no market or stakeholder pressure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107720.0,
      "end_time": 109696.0,
      "text": "and employees were so surprised"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109720.0,
      "end_time": 112200.0,
      "text": "that they burst into tears when they heard the news."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113600.0,
      "end_time": 116919.0,
      "text": "Actions like Ulukaya&#39;s are beautiful because they catch us off guard."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117480.0,
      "end_time": 119976.0,
      "text": "They create something out of nothing"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120000.0,
      "end_time": 122240.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re completely unnecessary."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124400.0,
      "end_time": 126960.0,
      "text": "I once worked at a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126120.0,
      "end_time": 127696.0,
      "text": "that was the result of a merger"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 127720.0,
      "end_time": 131376.0,
      "text": "of a large IT outsourcing firm and a small design firm."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131400.0,
      "end_time": 133376.0,
      "text": "We were merging 9,000 software engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133400.0,
      "end_time": 135160.0,
      "text": "with 1,000 creative types."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135800.0,
      "end_time": 138536.0,
      "text": "And to unify these immensely different cultures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138560.0,
      "end_time": 141616.0,
      "text": "we were going to launch a third, new brand."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141639.0,
      "end_time": 145136.0,
      "text": "And the new brand color was going to be orange."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145160.0,
      "end_time": 148576.0,
      "text": "And as we were going through the budget for the rollouts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148600.0,
      "end_time": 150656.0,
      "text": "we decided last minute"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150680.0,
      "end_time": 154336.0,
      "text": "to cut the purchase of 10,000 orange balloons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154360.0,
      "end_time": 157160.0,
      "text": "which we had meant to distribute to all staff worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 157800.0,
      "end_time": 160960.0,
      "text": "They just seemed unnecessary and cute in the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161920.0,
      "end_time": 163815.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know back then"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163840.0,
      "end_time": 166376.0,
      "text": "that our decision marked the beginning of the end --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166400.0,
      "end_time": 169400.0,
      "text": "that these two organizations would never become one."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 169920.0,
      "end_time": 172616.0,
      "text": "And sure enough, the merger eventually failed."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172640.0,
      "end_time": 175456.0,
      "text": "Now, was it because there weren&#39;t any orange balloons?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 175480.0,
      "end_time": 177790.0,
      "text": "No, of course not."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 177880.0,
      "end_time": 181920.0,
      "text": "But the kill-the-orange-balloons mentality permeated everything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183120.0,
      "end_time": 186896.0,
      "text": "You might not always realize it, but when you cut the unnecessary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186920.0,
      "end_time": 188399.0,
      "text": "you cut everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189280.0,
      "end_time": 193800.0,
      "text": "Leading with beauty means rising above what is merely necessary."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 194760.0,
      "end_time": 197920.0,
      "text": "So do not kill your orange balloons."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 199400.0,
      "end_time": 200696.0,
      "text": "The second principle:"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200720.0,
      "end_time": 202560.0,
      "text": "create intimacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202800.0,
      "end_time": 203456.0,
      "text": "[Create Intimacy]"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 203480.0,
      "end_time": 206296.0,
      "text": "Studies show that how we feel about our workplace"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206320.0,
      "end_time": 209400.0,
      "text": "very much depends on the relationships with our coworkers."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209680.0,
      "end_time": 213960.0,
      "text": "And what are relationships other than a string of microinteractions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 213120.0,
      "end_time": 216336.0,
      "text": "There are hundreds of these every day in our organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216360.0,
      "end_time": 220640.0,
      "text": "that have the potential to distinguish a good life from a beautiful one."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 221480.0,
      "end_time": 223456.0,
      "text": "The marriage researcher John Gottman says"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 223480.0,
      "end_time": 226960.0,
      "text": "that the secret of a healthy relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226120.0,
      "end_time": 229176.0,
      "text": "is not the great gesture or the lofty promise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 229200.0,
      "end_time": 231399.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s small moments of attachment."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232200.0,
      "end_time": 233880.0,
      "text": "In other words, intimacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235120.0,
      "end_time": 236656.0,
      "text": "In our networked organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 236680.0,
      "end_time": 239296.0,
      "text": "we tout the strength of weak ties"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 239320.0,
      "end_time": 242176.0,
      "text": "but we underestimate the strength of strong ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 242200.0,
      "end_time": 245950.0,
      "text": "We forget the words of the writer Richard Bach who once said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 245120.0,
      "end_time": 246336.0,
      "text": "\"Intimacy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 246360.0,
      "end_time": 247576.0,
      "text": "not connectedness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 247600.0,
      "end_time": 249920.0,
      "text": "intimacy is the opposite of loneliness.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 250920.0,
      "end_time": 254280.0,
      "text": "So how do we design for organizational intimacy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 255480.0,
      "end_time": 257336.0,
      "text": "The humanitarian organization CARE"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 257360.0,
      "end_time": 259736.0,
      "text": "wanted to launch a campaign on gender equality"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 259760.0,
      "end_time": 261240.0,
      "text": "in villages in northern India."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 262120.0,
      "end_time": 263376.0,
      "text": "But it realized quickly"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 263400.0,
      "end_time": 266359.0,
      "text": "that it had to have this conversation first with its own staff."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 266960.0,
      "end_time": 272150.0,
      "text": "So it invited all 36 team members and their partners"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 272400.0,
      "end_time": 273776.0,
      "text": "to one of the Khajuraho Temples,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 273800.0,
      "end_time": 276560.0,
      "text": "known for their famous erotic sculptures."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 277520.0,
      "end_time": 281960.0,
      "text": "And there they openly discussed their personal relationships --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 281120.0,
      "end_time": 283680.0,
      "text": "their own experiences of gender equality"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 284520.0,
      "end_time": 287150.0,
      "text": "with the coworkers and the partners."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287400.0,
      "end_time": 289336.0,
      "text": "It was eye-opening for the participants."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289360.0,
      "end_time": 293376.0,
      "text": "Not only did it allow them to relate to the communities they serve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293400.0,
      "end_time": 295936.0,
      "text": "it also broke down invisible barriers"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 295960.0,
      "end_time": 298176.0,
      "text": "and created a lasting bond amongst themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 298200.0,
      "end_time": 301960.0,
      "text": "Not a single team member quit in the next four years."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 303200.0,
      "end_time": 305159.0,
      "text": "So this is how you create intimacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 305720.0,
      "end_time": 307800.0,
      "text": "No masks ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 307920.0,
      "end_time": 309536.0,
      "text": "or lots of masks."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 309560.0,
      "end_time": 310776.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 310800.0,
      "end_time": 312256.0,
      "text": "When Danone, the food company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 312280.0,
      "end_time": 315840.0,
      "text": "wanted to translate its new company manifesto into product initiatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 316520.0,
      "end_time": 318695.0,
      "text": "it gathered the management team"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 318720.0,
      "end_time": 322336.0,
      "text": "and 100 employees from across different departments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 322360.0,
      "end_time": 323976.0,
      "text": "seniority levels and regions"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 324000.0,
      "end_time": 326120.0,
      "text": "for a three-day strategy retreat."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 326800.0,
      "end_time": 330256.0,
      "text": "And it asked everybody to wear costumes for the entire meeting:"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 330280.0,
      "end_time": 333376.0,
      "text": "wigs, crazy hats, feather boas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 333400.0,
      "end_time": 334799.0,
      "text": "huge glasses and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 335560.0,
      "end_time": 337816.0,
      "text": "And they left with concrete outcomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 337840.0,
      "end_time": 339520.0,
      "text": "and full of enthusiasm."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 340400.0,
      "end_time": 343160.0,
      "text": "And when I asked the woman who had designed this experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 343400.0,
      "end_time": 344256.0,
      "text": "why it worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 344280.0,
      "end_time": 348950.0,
      "text": "she simply said, \"Never underestimate the power of a ridiculous wig.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 348120.0,
      "end_time": 349296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 349320.0,
      "end_time": 351680.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 352880.0,
      "end_time": 356560.0,
      "text": "Because wigs erase hierarchy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 356800.0,
      "end_time": 357936.0,
      "text": "and hierarchy kills intimacy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 357960.0,
      "end_time": 359176.0,
      "text": "both ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 359200.0,
      "end_time": 360880.0,
      "text": "for the CEO and the intern."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 361440.0,
      "end_time": 365576.0,
      "text": "Wigs allow us to use the disguise of the false"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 365600.0,
      "end_time": 368400.0,
      "text": "to show something true about ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 369120.0,
      "end_time": 371336.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s not easy in our everyday work lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 371360.0,
      "end_time": 373696.0,
      "text": "because the relationship with our organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 373720.0,
      "end_time": 377600.0,
      "text": "is often like that of a married couple that has grown apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 378240.0,
      "end_time": 381256.0,
      "text": "suffered betrayals and disappointments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 381280.0,
      "end_time": 384599.0,
      "text": "and is now desperate to be beautiful for one another once again."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 385880.0,
      "end_time": 389360.0,
      "text": "And for either of us the first step towards beauty involves a huge risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 390520.0,
      "end_time": 391736.0,
      "text": "The risk to be ugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 391760.0,
      "end_time": 393960.0,
      "text": "[Be Ugly]"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 393120.0,
      "end_time": 397376.0,
      "text": "So many organizations these days are keen on designing beautiful workplaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 397400.0,
      "end_time": 399150.0,
      "text": "that look like anything but work:"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 399400.0,
      "end_time": 403560.0,
      "text": "vacation resorts, coffee shops, playgrounds or college campuses --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 403800.0,
      "end_time": 404296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 404320.0,
      "end_time": 406496.0,
      "text": "Based on the promises of positive psychology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 406520.0,
      "end_time": 409895.0,
      "text": "we speak of play and gamification,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 409920.0,
      "end_time": 413456.0,
      "text": "and one start-up even says that when someone gets fired,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 413480.0,
      "end_time": 414776.0,
      "text": "they have graduated."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 414800.0,
      "end_time": 416776.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 416800.0,
      "end_time": 420296.0,
      "text": "That kind of beautiful language only goes \"skin deep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 420320.0,
      "end_time": 423560.0,
      "text": "but ugly cuts clean to the bone,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 424240.0,
      "end_time": 426456.0,
      "text": "as the writer Dorothy Parker once put it."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 426480.0,
      "end_time": 430000.0,
      "text": "To be authentic is to be ugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 430800.0,
      "end_time": 435216.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t mean that you can&#39;t have fun or must give in to the vulgar or cynical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 435240.0,
      "end_time": 438640.0,
      "text": "but it does mean that you speak the actual ugly truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 439760.0,
      "end_time": 441150.0,
      "text": "Like this manufacturer"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 441400.0,
      "end_time": 444776.0,
      "text": "that wanted to transform one of its struggling business units."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 444800.0,
      "end_time": 448216.0,
      "text": "It identified, named and pinned on large boards all the issues --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 448240.0,
      "end_time": 449896.0,
      "text": "and there were hundreds of them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 449920.0,
      "end_time": 452216.0,
      "text": "that had become obstacles to better performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 452240.0,
      "end_time": 454816.0,
      "text": "They put them on boards, moved them all into one room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 454840.0,
      "end_time": 457950.0,
      "text": "which they called \"the ugly room.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 457120.0,
      "end_time": 459496.0,
      "text": "The ugly became visible for everyone to see --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 459520.0,
      "end_time": 461335.0,
      "text": "it was celebrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 461360.0,
      "end_time": 465216.0,
      "text": "And the ugly room served as a mix of mirror exhibition and operating room --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 465240.0,
      "end_time": 468760.0,
      "text": "a biopsy on the living flesh to cut out all the bureaucracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 470640.0,
      "end_time": 473840.0,
      "text": "The ugliest part of our body is our brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 474640.0,
      "end_time": 477176.0,
      "text": "Literally and neurologically."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 477200.0,
      "end_time": 480440.0,
      "text": "Our brain renders ugly what is unfamiliar ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 481440.0,
      "end_time": 483416.0,
      "text": "modern art, atonal music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 483440.0,
      "end_time": 484656.0,
      "text": "jazz, maybe --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 484680.0,
      "end_time": 486376.0,
      "text": "VR goggles for that matter --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 486400.0,
      "end_time": 489479.0,
      "text": "strange objects, sounds and people."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 490320.0,
      "end_time": 492496.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;ve all been ugly once."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 492520.0,
      "end_time": 494200.0,
      "text": "We were a weird-looking baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 494880.0,
      "end_time": 497159.0,
      "text": "a new kid on the block, a foreigner."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 497960.0,
      "end_time": 501440.0,
      "text": "And we will be ugly again when we don&#39;t belong."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 503320.0,
      "end_time": 505216.0,
      "text": "The Center for Political Beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 505240.0,
      "end_time": 506856.0,
      "text": "an activist collective in Berlin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 506880.0,
      "end_time": 509560.0,
      "text": "recently staged an extreme artistic intervention."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 510200.0,
      "end_time": 512960.0,
      "text": "With the permission of relatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 512120.0,
      "end_time": 516256.0,
      "text": "it exhumed the corpses of refugees who had drowned at Europe&#39;s borders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 516280.0,
      "end_time": 518175.0,
      "text": "transported them all the way to Berlin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 518200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521000.00000000006,
      "text": "and then reburied them at the heart of the German capital."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 522400.0,
      "end_time": 526960.0,
      "text": "The idea was to allow them to reach their desired destination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 526120.0,
      "end_time": 527760.0,
      "text": "if only after their death."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 528960.0,
      "end_time": 531976.0,
      "text": "Such acts of beautification may not be pretty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 532000.0,
      "end_time": 533256.0,
      "text": "but they are much needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 533280.0,
      "end_time": 536736.0,
      "text": "Because things tend to get ugly when there&#39;s only one meaning, one truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 536760.0,
      "end_time": 538200.0,
      "text": "only answers and no questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 538880.0,
      "end_time": 541880.0,
      "text": "Beautiful organizations keep asking questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 542480.0,
      "end_time": 544600.0,
      "text": "They remain incomplete,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 545275.0,
      "end_time": 547656.0,
      "text": "which is the fourth and the last of the principles."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 547680.0,
      "end_time": 549215.0,
      "text": "[Remain Incomplete]"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 549240.0,
      "end_time": 550560.0,
      "text": "Recently I was in Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 551400.0,
      "end_time": 554376.0,
      "text": "and a friend of mine took me to Nuit Debout,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 554400.0,
      "end_time": 555935.0,
      "text": "which stands for \"up all night,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 555960.0,
      "end_time": 557896.0,
      "text": "the self-organized protest movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 557920.0,
      "end_time": 561839.0,
      "text": "that had formed in response to the proposed labor laws in France."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 562680.0,
      "end_time": 565896.0,
      "text": "Every night, hundreds gathered at the Place de la République."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 565920.0,
      "end_time": 568496.0,
      "text": "Every night they set up a small, temporary village"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 568520.0,
      "end_time": 571120.0,
      "text": "to deliberate their own vision of the French Republic."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 572120.0,
      "end_time": 574776.0,
      "text": "And at the core of this adhocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 574800.0,
      "end_time": 577550.0,
      "text": "was a general assembly where anybody could speak"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 577800.0,
      "end_time": 579680.0,
      "text": "using a specially designed sign language."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 580920.0,
      "end_time": 584175.0,
      "text": "Like Occupy Wall Street and other protest movements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 584200.0,
      "end_time": 587960.0,
      "text": "Nuit Debout was born in the face of crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 587120.0,
      "end_time": 588576.0,
      "text": "It was messy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 588600.0,
      "end_time": 590920.0,
      "text": "full of controversies and contradictions."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 591920.0,
      "end_time": 594695.0,
      "text": "But whether you agreed with the movement&#39;s goals or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 594720.0,
      "end_time": 598440.0,
      "text": "every gathering was a beautiful lesson in raw humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 599640.0,
      "end_time": 601656.0,
      "text": "And how fitting that Paris --"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 601680.0,
      "end_time": 604455.0,
      "text": "the city of ideals, the city of beauty --"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 604480.0,
      "end_time": 605696.0,
      "text": "was it&#39;s stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 605720.0,
      "end_time": 607536.0,
      "text": "It reminds us that like great cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 607560.0,
      "end_time": 611736.0,
      "text": "the most beautiful organizations are ideas worth fighting for --"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 611760.0,
      "end_time": 614800.0,
      "text": "even and especially when their outcome is uncertain."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 615480.0,
      "end_time": 616776.0,
      "text": "They are movements;"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 616800.0,
      "end_time": 619136.0,
      "text": "they are always imperfect, never fully organized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 619160.0,
      "end_time": 621856.0,
      "text": "so they avoid ever becoming banal."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 621880.0,
      "end_time": 624216.0,
      "text": "They have something but we don&#39;t know what it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 624240.0,
      "end_time": 627176.0,
      "text": "They remain mysterious; we can&#39;t take our eyes off them."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 627200.0,
      "end_time": 629160.0,
      "text": "We find them beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 631240.0,
      "end_time": 633960.0,
      "text": "So to do the unnecessary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 633120.0,
      "end_time": 634776.0,
      "text": "to create intimacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 634800.0,
      "end_time": 636295.0,
      "text": "to be ugly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 636320.0,
      "end_time": 637880.0,
      "text": "to remain incomplete --"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 638560.0,
      "end_time": 641536.0,
      "text": "these are not only the qualities of beautiful organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 641560.0,
      "end_time": 644000.0,
      "text": "these are inherently human characteristics."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 644600.0,
      "end_time": 648240.0,
      "text": "And these are also the qualities of what we call home."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 649520.0,
      "end_time": 651936.0,
      "text": "And as we disrupt, and are disrupted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 651960.0,
      "end_time": 654256.0,
      "text": "the least we can do is to ensure"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 654280.0,
      "end_time": 658295.0,
      "text": "that we still feel at home in our organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 658320.0,
      "end_time": 661720.0,
      "text": "and that we use our organizations to create that feeling for others."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 662600.0,
      "end_time": 665696.0,
      "text": "Beauty can save the world when we embrace these principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 665720.0,
      "end_time": 667200.0,
      "text": "and design for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 668160.0,
      "end_time": 671376.0,
      "text": "In the face of artificial intelligence and machine learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 671400.0,
      "end_time": 673736.0,
      "text": "we need a new radical humanism."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 673760.0,
      "end_time": 678160.0,
      "text": "We must acquire and promote a new aesthetic and sentimental education."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 679320.0,
      "end_time": 680680.0,
      "text": "Because if we don&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 681360.0,
      "end_time": 683816.0,
      "text": "we might end up feeling like aliens"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 683840.0,
      "end_time": 687856.0,
      "text": "in organizations and societies that are full of smart machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 687880.0,
      "end_time": 690696.0,
      "text": "that have no appreciation whatsoever"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 690720.0,
      "end_time": 692336.0,
      "text": "for the unnecessary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 692360.0,
      "end_time": 693616.0,
      "text": "the intimate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 693640.0,
      "end_time": 695336.0,
      "text": "the incomplete"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 695360.0,
      "end_time": 697400.0,
      "text": "and definitely not for the ugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 697760.0,
      "end_time": 698976.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 699000.0,
      "end_time": 703862.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}